style.art_style: Chibi, cartoon, simplified illustration, sticker art, flat design
style.technique: Digital illustration, thick black outlines, flat colors, minimal shading, subtle texture or light gradient on specific elements (e.g., hair, hat), vector art style
style.color_palette: Limited and consistent palette of warm browns (hair, hat, vest, shorts, shoes), white (shirt), light skin tones with prominent rosy cheeks, and a pop of red (neck accessory). Overall soft and muted, with strong contrast from outlines.
style.lighting: Flat, even, diffused lighting with no discernible shadows or highlights, giving a bright and clean appearance.
style.mood: Cute, innocent, childlike, highly expressive, cheerful, pensive, sad, angry.

character.hair: Short, medium brown, bowl-cut or mushroom-cut style, with simple, rounded strands.
character.eyes: Large, solid black, oval or circular shapes, without pupils or irises. Very simplified.
character.face: Round, soft, with prominent rosy cheeks. Small oval nose and simple line mouth that changes dynamically with expression.
character.outfit: White long-sleeved shirt, brown vest, brown shorts, brown shoes with white sock-like cuffs.
character.accessories: Brown beret or flat cap, small red neck accessory (bow tie or bandana).
character.body_proportions: Chibi style, approximately 2.5-head proportion, where the entire body height is roughly two and a half times the height of the head.
character.limb_proportions: Very short and thick, stubby limbs. Arms extend to about waist level. Legs are short and compact, with particularly short visible lower legs, contributing to the overall compact, chibi appearance.
character.torso_shape: Short, wide, and somewhat rectangular or barrel-shaped, with little to no waist definition.
character.hand_style: Simplified, rounded mitten-style or blob-like, with no individual fingers clearly defined. Hands are used to convey simple gestures.

composition.pose: Dynamic and highly expressive full-body poses, often conveying strong emotions (e.g., jumping, crying, thinking, smiling, angry, squatting).
composition.angle: Eye-level or slightly low-angle, focusing on the full character.
composition.background: Plain white or transparent background, with no environmental elements.
composition.depth_of_field: Flat depth of field; all elements are in sharp focus with no blur.

analysis.negative_prompt: realistic proportions, detailed anatomy, mature, adult, elongated limbs, thin body, complex shading, strong gradients, photorealistic, 3D render, sharp shadows, detailed background, multiple characters, complex textures, thin outlines, realistic eyes, pupils, irises, detailed fingers, individual fingers, varied outfits, complex facial features, complex clothing details, strong highlights, transparent elements
